# act configuration: map GitHub-hosted runner labels to local Docker images.
#
# `catthehacker/ubuntu:act-24.04` is the medium-sized image (~1.7 GB) and
# includes Python and standard tools — sufficient for our pure-Python
# workflows that install their own toolchain via setup-uv.
#
# Per-user overrides live in `.actrc.local` (gitignored).
-P ubuntu-24.04=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-24.04
